Text Quality Checker. Checks for:
	* Spellings
	* Structure and Grammar
	* Language flow - Coherence (Coming soon :D)
	* Other linguistic features of the Essay (TBD).

DEPENDENCIES:
	* Link Parser - http://www.link.cs.cmu.edu/link/

	* Python and Libraries
	1) Python 3.x
	2) Pyenchant - http://packages.python.org/pyenchant/api/enchant.html
	3) Natural Language Toolkit - http://nltk.googlecode.com/files/nltk-2.0.1rc1.tar.gz
